question: Which restaurant is available towards Bowditch Middle School Auditorium, Foster City, CA within 30 kilometers from Northeastern University Silicon Valley, San Jose, CA?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-121.889552 37.33709)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-122.248613 37.559053)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'restaurant'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-121.889552 37.33709)',4326)::geography, 30000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-121.889552 37.33709)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);
